<feature
      id="org.eclipse.epsilon.emf.dt.feature"
      label="Epsilon Development Tools for EMF"
      version="2.2.0.202009032353"
      provider-name="Eclipse Modeling Project">

   <description url="http://www.eclipse.org/epsilon">
      This feature provides the Epsilon development tools needed to work with EMF models. These include:
- The EPackage Registry view for querying all registered EPackages.
- The reflective Exeed editor and the ModeLink model weaving editor.
- Apache Ant tasks for working with EMF models in Epsilon.
- EUnit extensions for comparing EMF models and showing their differences from the EUnit view.
   </description>

